{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Custom application language for push notifications."}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"language"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:SS","text":"String","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":" { ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"keyword","text":"get"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"set","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" }","kind":"text"}],"languages":["swift"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Overview","anchor":"Overview"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Override the device language for notification content localization. This affects which language version of your push notifications is delivered from Pushwoosh servers."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":2,"text":"Format","anchor":"Format","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Use lowercase two-letter ISO-639-1 language codes:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"code":"\"en\"","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" - English"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"code":"\"de\"","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" - German"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"code":"\"fr\"","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" - French","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"\"es\""},{"type":"text","text":" - Spanish"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"\"ru\""},{"type":"text","text":" - Russian"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"\"ja\""},{"text":" - Japanese","type":"text"}]}]}]},{"level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Default Behavior","anchor":"Default-Behavior"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"By default, Pushwoosh uses the device’s system language. Set this property to override, or set to ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"nil"},{"type":"text","text":" to revert to device language."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Example","anchor":"Example","type":"heading","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Let user choose notification language:"}]},{"code":["func updateNotificationLanguage(_ languageCode: String) {","    Pushwoosh.configure.language = languageCode","","    userDefaults.set(languageCode, forKey: \"notificationLanguage\")","}"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Sync with app’s localization:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"codeListing","code":["func application(_ application: UIApplication,","                didFinishLaunchingWithOptions launchOptions: [UIApplication.LaunchOptionsKey: Any]?) -> Bool {","","    if let appLanguage = Bundle.main.preferredLocalizations.first {","        Pushwoosh.configure.language = appLanguage","    }","","    Pushwoosh.configure.registerForPushNotifications()","","    return true","}"],"syntax":"swift"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Language selection in settings:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["class LanguageSettingsViewController: UIViewController {","","    let languages = [","        (\"en\", \"English\"),","        (\"de\", \"Deutsch\"),","        (\"fr\", \"Français\"),","        (\"es\", \"Español\")","    ]","","    func tableView(_ tableView: UITableView, didSelectRowAt indexPath: IndexPath) {","        let (code, _) = languages[indexPath.row]","","        Pushwoosh.configure.language = code","","        Bundle.setLanguage(code)","","        reloadApp()","    }","}"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"}]}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"kind":"symbol","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshiOS\/documentation\/PushwooshFramework","doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshiOS\/documentation\/PushwooshFramework\/Pushwoosh"]]}